NAME
  atpl - transpile Aurora sugar to plain Lua

SYNOPSIS
  atpl <in.lua> [out.lua]

DESCRIPTION
  Adds compound assignment operators (+= -= *= /= //= %= ^= ..= &= |= <<= >>=).
  Line-oriented: the left-hand side is duplicated, so index expressions with
  side effects are evaluated twice. Plain Lua files pass through unchanged.
